{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about/publication-scheme","content_id":"5f54e9fa-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"Every government department has a publication scheme, which makes information available to the public about how it operates and how it spends its budget. ","details":{"attachments":[{"accessible":false,"alternative_format_contact_email":"accessible.formats@dwp.gov.uk","assets":[{"asset_manager_id":"5a7c0250e5274a7318b9078f","filename":"jsa-guide-chapter-guide-270913.pdf"}],"attachment_type":"file","content_type":"application/pdf","file_size":36093,"filename":"jsa-guide-chapter-guide-270913.pdf","id":"8977536","number_of_pages":3,"title":"Jobseeker’s Allowance procedural guidance – chapter guide","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a7c0250e5274a7318b9078f/jsa-guide-chapter-guide-270913.pdf"},{"accessible":false,"alternative_format_contact_email":"accessible.formats@dwp.gov.uk","assets":[{"asset_manager_id":"5a78ad9be5274a2acd188f1c","filename":"lmc-guide-chapter-guide.pdf"}],"attachment_type":"file","content_type":"application/pdf","file_size":23442,"filename":"lmc-guide-chapter-guide.pdf","id":"8977537","number_of_pages":1,"title":"Labour market conditions guide – chapter guide","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a78ad9be5274a2acd188f1c/lmc-guide-chapter-guide.pdf"}],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>You don’t need to make a Freedom of Information (<abbr title=\"Freedom of Information\">FOI</abbr>) request for this information.</p>\n\n<p>We have used the subject headings recommended by the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://ico.org.uk/\">Information Commissioner’s Office</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"who-we-are-and-what-we-do\">Who we are and what we do</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"our-work\">Our work</h3>\n\n<p>The information we publish is set into classes. These classes are:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about\">what we do</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&amp;publication_filter_option=transparency-data&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">transparency</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/announcements?keywords=&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">announcements</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/announcements?keywords=speech&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">speeches</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"roles-and-responsibilities\">Roles and responsibilities</h3>\n\n<p>Information about roles and responsibilities at <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> includes:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions#ministers\">ministers</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions#management\">management</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"policy-development\">Policy development</h3>\n\n<p>You can find out about our policies at:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/policies?keywords=&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">policies</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&amp;publication_filter_option=policy-papers&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">policy publications</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"legislation\">Legislation</h3>\n\n<p>Information about the legislation that impacts on <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> policies is available at <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.legislation.gov.uk/\">legislation.gov.uk</a>.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"organisations-the-department-is-responsible-for-sponsors-or-works-in-partnership-with\">Organisations the department is responsible for, sponsors or works in partnership with</h3>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations#department-for-work-pensions\">Organisations <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> works with</a> include a number of agencies and public bodies.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"contacting-the-department\">Contacting the department</h3>\n\n<p>Visit <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions#org-contacts\">contact us</a> for all <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> contact details.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"what-we-spend-and-how-we-spend-it\">What we spend and how we spend it</h2>\n\n<p>Information about what we spend includes:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>audit reports</li>\n  <li>pay and grading structures</li>\n  <li>hospitality and expenses</li>\n  <li>payments to suppliers</li>\n  <li>information about contracts</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We publish this information in:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&amp;publication_filter_option=corporate-reports&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">corporate reports</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&amp;publication_filter_option=transparency-data&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">transparency publications</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about/procurement/\">procurement procedures</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"our-priorities\">Our priorities</h2>\n\n<p>Read about <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about#priorities\">our priorities</a> to find out what we’re focusing on and how we’re doing.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"how-we-make-decisions\">How we make decisions</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"major-policy-proposals-and-decisions\">Major policy proposals and decisions</h3>\n\n<p>Read <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/policies?keywords=&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">our policies</a> to find out about our policy objectives and decisions.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"public-consultations-and-government-responses\">Public consultations and government responses</h3>\n\n<p>Read our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&amp;publication_filter_option=consultations&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">open and closed public consultations</a> on GOV.UK.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"impact-assessments\">Impact assessments</h3>\n\n<p>Access our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&amp;publication_filter_option=impact-assessments&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">impact assessments</a> on GOV.UK.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"background-information-for-major-policy-proposals-and-decisions\">Background information for major policy proposals and decisions</h3>\n\n<p>Information we gather to inform our policy proposals and decisions includes:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&amp;publication_filter_option=research-and-analysis&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">research</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about/statistics\">statistics</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&amp;publication_filter_option=impact-assessments&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">impact assessments</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&amp;publication_filter_option=policy-papers&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">policy publications</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"meetings\">Meetings</h3>\n\n<p>We publish information about:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/dwp-ministers-hospitality-and-gifts\"><abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> meetings with external organisations</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/dwp-special-advisers-hospitality-and-gifts\">special advisers’ meetings</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"internal-manuals-and-guidance\">Internal manuals and guidance</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&amp;publication_filter_option=guidance&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">internal manuals and guidance</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"our-policies-and-procedures\">Our policies and procedures</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"customer-service\">Customer service</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about/complaints-procedure\">complaints and appeals</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&amp;publication_filter_option=foi-releases&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">freedom of information</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"information-management-and-personal-data-policies\">Information management and personal data policies</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about/personal-information-charter\">privacy policy and data protection</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dwp-procurement-security-policies-and-standards\">data protection and information security for suppliers</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dwp-information-management-policies\">information management policy</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/transgender-customers-summary-of-dwps-policy-in-respect-of-the-retention-of-information\">transgender customers: summary of <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr>’s policy in respect of the retention of information</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dwp-data-strategy-2023-to-2030\"><abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> Data Strategy 2023 to 2030</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"diversity-and-equality\">Diversity and equality</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about/equality-and-diversity\">diversity and equality</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"recruitment\">Recruitment</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about/recruitment\">recruitment standards and policies</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"internal-guidance\">Internal guidance</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"#jobseekers-allowance-jsa-procedural-guidance\">Jobseeker’s Allowance (<abbr title=\"Jobseeker’s Allowance\">JSA</abbr>) procedural guidance</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"#labour-market-conditions-guide\">labour market conditions guide</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/search?q=%3A+staff+guide&amp;filter_organisations[]=department-for-work-pensions\">other staff guides</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"lists-and-registers\">Lists and registers</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>information asset register</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications?keywords=&amp;publication_filter_option=foi-releases&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">information released under the Freedom of Information Act</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"the-services-we-offer\">The services we offer</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"services-for-members-of-the-public\">Services for members of the public</h3>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> provides its customer services through <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about#who-we-are\">operational organisations</a>.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"services-for-partners-and-stakeholders\">Services for partners and stakeholders</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/healthcare-practitioners-guidance-and-information-from-dwp\">healthcare professionals</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/housing-benefit-information-guidance-and-good-practice-for-local-authority-staff\">local authority staff</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"information-products\">Information products</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>leaflets</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/browse/benefits\">claim forms</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"media-releases\">Media releases</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/announcements?keywords=&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">announcements</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/announcements?keywords=speech&amp;topics[]=all&amp;departments[]=department-for-work-pensions\">speeches</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"guides-available-on-request\">Guides available on request</h2>\n<p>Some <abbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\">DWP</abbr> publications are not available on the website. But you can ask the owner of the guide for a copy.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"jobseekers-allowance-jsa-procedural-guidance\">Jobseeker’s Allowance (<abbr title=\"Jobseeker’s Allowance\">JSA</abbr>) procedural guidance</h3>\n\n<p>This guidance is for <abbr title=\"Jobseeker’s Allowance\">JSA</abbr> processors and other <abbr title=\"Jobseeker’s Allowance\">JSA</abbr> staff. It provides end-to-end guidance on processing <abbr title=\"Jobseeker’s Allowance\">JSA</abbr> claims. This guide is a large document consisting of a number of chapters. When requesting a copy of this, please tell us which chapters you are interested in.</p>\n\n<section data-module=\"ga4-link-tracker\" class=\"gem-c-attachment govuk-!-margin-bottom-6\">\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail govuk-!-display-none-print\">\n    <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a7c0250e5274a7318b9078f/jsa-guide-chapter-guide-270913.pdf\"